\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\NormalTok{train_indeks <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{createDataPartition}\NormalTok{(dataframe}\OperatorTok{$}\NormalTok{cancer_c, }\DataTypeTok{p =} \FloatTok{0.8}\NormalTok{, }\DataTypeTok{list =} \OtherTok{FALSE}\NormalTok{, }\DataTypeTok{times =} \DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{)}

\NormalTok{train <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{dataframe[train_indeks,]}
\NormalTok{test <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{dataframe[}\OperatorTok{-}\NormalTok{train_indeks,]}

\NormalTok{train_x <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{train }\OperatorTok{%>%}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{dplyr}\OperatorTok{::}\KeywordTok{select}\NormalTok{(}\OperatorTok{-}\NormalTok{cancer_c)}
\NormalTok{train_y <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{train}\OperatorTok{$}\NormalTok{cancer_c}

\NormalTok{test_x <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{test }\OperatorTok{%>%}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{dplyr}\OperatorTok{::}\KeywordTok{select}\NormalTok{(}\OperatorTok{-}\NormalTok{cancer_c)}
\NormalTok{test_y <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{test}\OperatorTok{$}\NormalTok{cancer_c}
\CommentTok{# eğitim verisinin hem bagimli hem de bagimsiz degiskenlerini tuttugumuz bir dataframe}
\NormalTok{training <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{data.frame}\NormalTok{(train_x, }\DataTypeTok{cancer_c =}\NormalTok{ train_y)}
\KeywordTok{head}\NormalTok{(training}\OperatorTok{$}\NormalTok{cancer_c)}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\section{KNN}\label{knn}

\subsection{Model}\label{model-1}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\CommentTok{# knn kategorik degiskenlerle calismaktadir bunun icin ya donusum yapilir ya da o kategorik degisken verisetinden cikarilir.}
\CommentTok{#install.packages("caret")}
\KeywordTok{library}\NormalTok{(caret)}
\NormalTok{train_indeks <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{createDataPartition}\NormalTok{(dataframe}\OperatorTok{$}\NormalTok{cancer_c, }\DataTypeTok{p =} \FloatTok{0.8}\NormalTok{, }\DataTypeTok{list =} \OtherTok{FALSE}\NormalTok{, }\DataTypeTok{times =} \DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{)}

\NormalTok{train <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{dataframe[train_indeks,]}
\NormalTok{test <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{dataframe[}\OperatorTok{-}\NormalTok{train_indeks,]}

\NormalTok{train_x <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{train }\OperatorTok{%>%}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{dplyr}\OperatorTok{::}\KeywordTok{select}\NormalTok{(}\OperatorTok{-}\NormalTok{cancer_c)}
\NormalTok{train_y <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{train}\OperatorTok{$}\NormalTok{cancer_c}

\NormalTok{test_x <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{test }\OperatorTok{%>%}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{dplyr}\OperatorTok{::}\KeywordTok{select}\NormalTok{(}\OperatorTok{-}\NormalTok{cancer_c)}
\NormalTok{test_y <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{test}\OperatorTok{$}\NormalTok{cancer_c}

\NormalTok{training <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{data.frame}\NormalTok{(train_x, }\DataTypeTok{cancer_c =}\NormalTok{ train_y)}

\NormalTok{knn_train <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{train}
\NormalTok{knn_test <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{test}

\NormalTok{knn_train <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{knn_train }\OperatorTok{%>%}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{select}\NormalTok{(}\OperatorTok{-}\NormalTok{cancer_c)}
\NormalTok{knn_test <-}\StringTok{ }\NormalTok{knn_test }\OperatorTok{%>%}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{select}\NormalTok{(}\OperatorTok{-}\NormalTok{cancer_c)}
\CommentTok{# knn fonksiyonu lojistik regresyon fonksiyonundan farkli degerlerle calisir}
\CommentTok{#install.packages("FNN")}
\KeywordTok{library}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"FNN"}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{knn_fit <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{knn}\NormalTok{(}\DataTypeTok{train =}\NormalTok{ knn_train, }\DataTypeTok{test =}\NormalTok{ knn_test, }\DataTypeTok{cl =}\NormalTok{ train_y, }\DataTypeTok{k =} \DecValTok{3}\NormalTok{)}
\KeywordTok{summary}\NormalTok{(knn_fit)}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\subsection{Model Tuning - Model
Optimizasyonu}\label{model-tuning---model-optimizasyonu-1}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\NormalTok{ctrl <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{trainControl}\NormalTok{(}\DataTypeTok{method =} \StringTok{"cv"}\NormalTok{, }
                     \DataTypeTok{number =} \DecValTok{10}\NormalTok{, }
                     \DataTypeTok{summaryFunction =}\NormalTok{ twoClassSummary,}
                     \DataTypeTok{classProbs =} \OtherTok{TRUE}\NormalTok{,}
                     \DataTypeTok{savePredictions =} \OtherTok{TRUE}\NormalTok{)}
\CommentTok{# bir arama vektoru olusturuldu}
\NormalTok{knn_grid <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{data.frame}\NormalTok{(}\DataTypeTok{k =} \KeywordTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\DecValTok{4}\OperatorTok{*}\NormalTok{(}\DecValTok{0}\OperatorTok{:}\DecValTok{5}\NormalTok{)}\OperatorTok{+}\DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{, }\DecValTok{20}\OperatorTok{*}\NormalTok{(}\DecValTok{1}\OperatorTok{:}\DecValTok{5}\NormalTok{)}\OperatorTok{+}\DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{, }\DecValTok{50}\OperatorTok{*}\NormalTok{(}\DecValTok{2}\OperatorTok{:}\DecValTok{9}\NormalTok{)}\OperatorTok{+}\DecValTok{1}\NormalTok{))}
\CommentTok{# 451 komsuluk degerinin en iyisi oldugu soylenmis}
\NormalTok{knn_tune <-}\StringTok{ }\KeywordTok{train}\NormalTok{(knn_test, test_y,}
                  \DataTypeTok{method =} \StringTok{"knn"}\NormalTok{,}
                  \DataTypeTok{metric =} \StringTok{"ROC"}\NormalTok{,}
                  \DataTypeTok{preProc =} \KeywordTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"center"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"scale"}\NormalTok{),}
                  \DataTypeTok{trControl =}\NormalTok{ ctrl,}
                  \DataTypeTok{tuneGrid =}\NormalTok{ knn_grid)}

\KeywordTok{plot}\NormalTok{(knn_tune)}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}
